If cosec&#8709;  – sin &#8709; = x and sec&#8709; – cos&#8709; = y, then find the value of x<sup>2</sup>y<sup>2</sup>(x<sup>2</sup> + y<sup>2</sup> + 3)? </br> यदि  cosec&#8709;  – sin &#8709; = x तथा  sec&#8709; – cos&#8709; = y हो,तो x<sup>2</sup>y<sup>2</sup>(x<sup>2</sup> + y<sup>2</sup> + 3) का मान क्या है ?
